    <h2>How to use this page</h2>
    <p>
        This page lets you manage the plugins of the AiiDAlab Quantum ESPRESSO app.
        Below, you will find all available plugins from the
        <a href="https://github.com/aiidalab/aiidalab-qe/blob/main/plugins.yaml" target="_blank"
            style="background-color: #ffdd57; padding: 2px 5px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">
            official AiiDAlab Quantum ESPRESSO plugin registry
        </a>.
    </p>
    <p>
        If you install a new plugin, you may need to <strong>refresh the calculation page</strong>
        for the newly installed functionality to appear.
    </p>
    <p>
        If you are developing a new plugin and would like to share it with the community,
        <a href="https://aiidalab-qe.readthedocs.io/development/plugin_registry.html" target="_blank"
            style="background-color: #ffdd57; padding: 2px 5px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">
            click here
        </a>
        to learn how to register it in the official plugin registry.
    </p>
    <p>
        You can install and uninstall plugins directly from this page.
    </p>

